{"ProductId":"10","Title":"Reserve<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Wood Limited Edition","ShortDescription":"Exceptional beauty, durability and energy efficiency","Description":"","ThumbnailImage":null,"ShowcaseImage":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/reserve-limimted-edition-design5-arch1-meranti-garage-door-595.webp?sfvrsn=d5180ef3_10","CanonicalUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/reserve","Overview":"<h3>A Stunning, Handcrafted Beauty</h3><h4>Hand-Built Wood Construction</h4><p>Choose from solid 4- or 5-layer craftsmanship, blending real wood overlays, optional tongue-and-groove base, insulating hemlock framing, and a smooth interior backer. It&rsquo;s a door built to last and look great for years.</p><h4>Genuine Wood, Responsibly Sourced</h4><p>Every door is made from sustainably harvested or naturally fallen wood, hand-selected for your region&rsquo;s climate.</p><h4>Completely Customizable</h4><p>Pick from eight classic carriage house looks, with options for decorative windows and hardware. Select your favorite from eight paint or stain-ready wood species or go bold with over 1,500 <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/colorblast\">Color Blast&reg; custom colors</a>.</p><h4>Built-In Comfort</h4><p><a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/garage-door-materials/insulation\">Polystyrene insulation</a> (R-value 5.9) helps keep your garage comfortable and energy bills lower, no matter the season.</p><h4>Ready for the Elements</h4><p>Need extra protection? Ask about <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/buyingguide/residential/windcode-residential-information\">WindCode&reg; reinforcement</a> for reliable performance in high-wind areas.</p><h4>Environmental Assurance</h4><p>Clopay doors are compliant with environmental laws and regulations. Clopay doors do not contain HFCs. All Clopay doors are compliant with:</p><ul><li>California SB 1013</li><li>Washington HB 1112 &ndash; Hydrofluorocarbon Greenhouse Gas Emissions</li><li>Canadian regulations amending the ozone-depleting substances and halocarbon alternatives regulations</li><li>New Jersey A-5583/S-3919 &ndash; Greenhouse Gas Bill</li></ul>","Options":"","Construction":"<h3>How It&rsquo;s Made: Reserve&reg; Wood Limited Edition</h3><p>Reserve&reg; Wood Limited Edition doors are all about solid construction and smart design. Each door features a polystyrene-insulated Hemlock frame, wrapped with a tough Luan interior backer for extra strength and energy efficiency. On the outside, hand-applied wood overlays, plus an optional tongue-and-groove base, deliver that unmistakable carriage house style. The doors might look like they swing out, but they operate overhead for everyday convenience.</p><p>The details set these doors apart: three-panel section construction allows for larger, authentic window openings, while a unique one-piece drip cap protects against moisture by keeping water away from grooved overlays. True divided windows come standard for that handcrafted look. Premium-grade hardware and tracks keep operation smooth and quiet, and a replaceable vinyl bottom seal (with optional aluminum retainer) blocks out the elements at the base. You get durability, weather resistance, and hassle-free maintenance, all in one standout door.</p><img sf-image-responsive=\"true\" src=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/about-us/cutaway-reserve-wood-limited-edition-5l.webp?sfvrsn=754574f2_1\" height=\"345\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;\" title=\"Cutaway-Reserve-Wood-Limited-Edition-5L\" width=\"400\" alt=\"Reserve Wood Limited Edition 5-Layer cutaway\" sf-size=\"10162\" /><br /><ol><li>Wood Overlay</li><li>Optional Base Material</li><li>Base Material</li><li>Polystyrene Insulated Hemlock Frame</li><li>2\" Luan Inside Skin</li></ol>","Models":"","FeaturesBenefits":"","SpringsHardware":"","GroupName":"","H1HeaderTitle":"Reserve Wood Limited Edition","DisplayIndex":16,"ImageGallery":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/image-gallery/reserve-wood-limited-edition","ColorDisclaimer":"<p>Give your garage door a look that&rsquo;s unique with a selection of classic stains and paint finishes. Choose from rich wood stains like Natural, Natural Oak, Cedar, Teak, Butternut, Mahogany, Dark Oak, Dark Oak Ebony Wash, and Ebony Wash, each designed to bring out the natural grain and character of Hemlock wood. Prefer a crisp, clean finish? The white paint option offers versatility and pairs well with almost any home.</p><p>All stains are hand-applied for depth and consistency, but keep in mind that color may appear slightly different depending on your screen and the wood&rsquo;s natural variations. There are also custom colors available on select models.</p><p><em>Clopay stain colors show on Hemlock wood. Note: Color may vary from on screen. Custom colors are available. Available on select models.</em></p>","TopSectionDisclaimer":"<p>Personalize your Reserve® Wood Limited Edition door with a range of top section and window options. Prefer a classic, understated look? Go with a solid top section for clean lines and timeless appeal. If you want to let in more natural light or add architectural flair, choose from several window shapes—rectangular, square, or arched—to match your home’s style.\r\nFrom simple divided panes to dramatic arched designs, each window option is crafted for both beauty and function.</p>\r\n<p>For double doors, there are special arched top sections that really make a statement across wider openings. Whether you love the elegance of curved arches or the simplicity of straight-edged glass, there’s a top section that fits your vision. Each option is designed to highlight the natural wood and bring even more character to your home’s exterior.</p>\r\n","HardwareDisclaimer":"<p>The finishing touch on your Reserve® Wood Limited Edition door is the hardware. Each door comes standard with spade lift handles, giving you a classic carriage house look right out of the box. But you can also upgrade to spear or colonial lift handles, try decorative lift handles for extra flair, or add a ring door knocker or twisted “L” handles for a custom feel. Escutcheon plates are also available for a polished, traditional accent.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\r\nStep plates are offered in matching spade, spear, or colonial styles, so your hardware ties the design together from top to bottom. Complete the look with coordinating strap hinges; choose from spade, spear, or colonial designs to match your handles and plates. All hardware options are built from durable materials and finished in classic black.</p>\r\n","DesignDisclaimer":"","RelatedProducts":[{"Title":"Canyon Ridge<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Carriage House (5-Layer)","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/cr5l-des11-rec13-tampa-showcase.webp?sfvrsn=d9bffbb6_1","Id":"30","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/canyonridge","DisplayIndex":3,"ShortDescription":"Insulated carriage house garage doors with faux wood composite cladding and overlays","AlternativeText":"Canyon Ridge Carriage House (5-Layer)"},{"Title":"Canyon Ridge<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Carriage House (4-Layer)","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/cr4l-d21-rec13-afp143r.webp?sfvrsn=8ae1d536_3","Id":"29","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/canyon-ridge-4-layer","DisplayIndex":4,"ShortDescription":"Stylish, low maintenance and insulated faux wood garage doors","AlternativeText":"Canyon Ridge Carriage House (4-Layer)"},{"Title":"Gallery<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Steel","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/gallery-steel-ug-long-rec14-595.webp?sfvrsn=a7ceae04_9","Id":"12","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/gallerysteel","DisplayIndex":8,"ShortDescription":"Grooved panel steel carriage house garage doors","AlternativeText":"Gallery Steel"},{"Title":"Coachman<sup class='sym